title: Paul Oakenfold - Trance Mission (Album) (VBRkbps) (2014)

Paul Oakenfold - Trance Mission (2014) 

                  Trance, Progressive, House | Perfecto Records

               VBR kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 02:33:43 | 299 Mb



Trance Mission includes twelve new Paul Oakenfold cover versions of some of the biggest, most iconic and influential electronic records of all time. This beautifully blended cocktail of styles and moods will strike a nerve with many; not only those that will recall the power and influence these songs had during their first life but also to those younger listeners that may be hearing of them for the first time. Perfecto Records & Armada are proud to announce the upcoming release of Paul Oakenfold's new album - Trance Mission - which will be released on June 20th 2014.
